		<td><b>Jim Power is Officially coming to NES.</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Hello Guys,<br /><br />Just wanted to give the heads up of our new and upcoming NES Homebrew.<br /><br />Jim Power Lost Dimension.<br /><br />We have been able to secure the rights of Jim Power and are working hard to get the game to the NES.<br /><br />Please check out this video footage<br /><br /><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OG5V-VWRtP0" class="postlink">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OG5V-VWRtP0</a><br /><br />NOTE: The Music if just a soundtrack, if you want to hear the NES soundtrack you can find it on the video description, or here:<br /><br /><a href="https://soundcloud.com/pichichi010/jim-power-nes-level-1-1" class="postlink">https://soundcloud.com/pichichi010/jim-power-nes-level-1-1</a><br /><br />Enjoy!

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


